# dotbins üß∞

![Build Status](https://github.com/basnijholt/dotbins/actions/workflows/pytest.yml/badge.svg)
[![Coverage](https://img.shields.io/codecov/c/github/basnijholt/dotbins)](https://codecov.io/gh/basnijholt/dotbins)
